<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="5May1937"><font color="red">5 May 1937</font> <i>NLJL</i> (from G. Wren Howard to Paul L&eacute;on): You express surprise that John Lane do not propose to use plates of ULYSSES already in existence &hellip; no plates do, in fact, exist, and because, even if they did, the corrections which you and Mr Joyce are naturally anxious to have made could only be made with difficulty on stereotypic plates </div>
